363f875c2a366","tid":1180034,"uid":63449,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:22:16.000Z","msg":"寧願無識過<br />\n但係佢既出現改變左我既人生<br />\n佢令我繼續讀返書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  甚至讀到上大學<br />\n令我多張社會大學入場卷<br />\n令我體會到好多我從未體會得到既事<br />\n<br />\n雖然佢成日都話自己唔好<br />\n雖然俾我揀多次我係會揀無識過<br />\n因為我知道 即使我同佢再次黎過 結局都係一樣<br />\n因為你唔會為左我而作出任何改變<br />\n但最少 這段情 我無後悔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你睇到既話 係啊 係我<br />\n我係同緊你講 希望你會幸福快樂 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f73b21cda42c5ab005c745529aacac2c307933f9","tid":1180034,"uid":247478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a001e940bfce4c4947322b16bbd47d567a653b77","tid":1180034,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T16:21:47.000Z","msg":"姐係對方會失憶？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T18:51:58.000Z","msg":"我都想"},{"pid":"cca29b659cb1146d017d66c4442f89d39d20b5d5","tid":1180034,"uid":51712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T19:10:25.000Z","msg":"求下你，比我經歷多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0012991d3293cec17f6a66073e62e50bd7e812","tid":1180034,"uid":221104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdf89c359585fd411ba2804b7184588ca271ce8b","tid":1180034,"uid":247478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"假設重新認識到最後都係同一個結果"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T19:25:09.000Z","msg":"重新無開始過，<br />\n亦無相遇過。<br />\n<br />\n不過人生係好撚殘酷，<br />\n冥冥冥之中自有主宰，<br />\n<br />\n「其實您死過一次才會學會愛，<br />\n其實您死過一次才會學會愛自己；<br />\n原來此生，<br />\n即是天堂。」"},{"pid":"0161ddb50d2a5b98616095e50abacf028cb48170","tid":1180034,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T19:33:15.000Z","msg":"未去到想從來無識過<br />\n不過點都唔會想重新認識過"},{"pid":"537cac074a4329babadef52d763a63be57cd7c8a","tid":1180034,"uid":89064,"like":0,"dislike":0,